{"tid":2490315,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不點名批黎智英壹傳媒兼披露被捕港台兼職記者過往刑事審訊記錄 鄧炳強言論涉藐視法庭","createTime":"2021-04-15T13:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T15:19:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1999970e310a895b9b3e9e826963eff8f7497ea2","tid":2490315,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"一、黎智英已經被正式檢控，並已進行一連串法律程序。此時，任何人發佈可能構成 real risk of prejudice to a fair trial 的言論/刊物/報道，都可能構成藐視法庭。<br />\n<br />\n二、至於什麼才算real risk of prejudice to a fair trial？其中一個例子就是發表關於被告的負面評論（&quot;No doubt the most serious form of contempt from the point of view of likely prejudice is the sort of case where a photograph is published of an accused, and adverse comment is made on him as an accused person in a particular trial.&quot;，見R v. Thomson Newspapers Ltd ex p AG [1968] 1 WLR 1）。<br />\n<br />\n三、鄧炳強今天的言論，明顯已是對於黎智英非常負面的評價。至於發佈其言論並附上黎智英照片的傳媒，因住佢遲啲告你藐視法庭。<br />\n<br />\n四、對於被捕的港台記者，雖然他未被正式檢控，但其實計算藐視法庭的時間，是可以早至由被捕的一刻計起（R v Clarke, ex p Crippen [1908-10] All ER Rep 915）。此時，發佈關於被捕人士的刑事紀錄會對他造成不公，可能構成藐視法庭（R v Parke [1903] 2 KB 432）。<br />\n<br />\n五、無論如何，即使法律上無法令鄧炳強入罪，但身為執法部門首長也不應主動發表可能影響公平審訊的言論，此乃非常接近犯法邊緣的舉動，並陷報道其言論的傳媒於不義。尤其是港台記者案件，披露其刑事紀錄根本毫無必要，除了是有意抹黑外，並沒有其他作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%89%B9%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E5%A3%B9%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92-%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E6%B6%89%E8%97%90%E8%A6%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A3%25B9%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2585%25BC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2597%2590%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwN7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=5354e0cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%25BB%259E%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A3%25B9%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E6%258A%25AB%25E9%259C%25B2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2585%25BC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2588%2591%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584-%25E9%2584%25A7%25E7%2582%25B3%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%2597%2590%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD%2F&h=0e19a8bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E9%BB%9E%E5%90%8D%E6%89%B9%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E5%A3%B9%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92-%E6%8A%AB%E9%9C%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B0%E5%85%BC%E8%81%B7%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E6%B6%89%E8%97%90%E8%A6%96%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"2a639b7e723bbb5b4e862b357ede4743c86b1bd4","tid":2490315,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13592c9e584a27ad2e9845841778910589085968","tid":2490315,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />